{"tid":2315122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港會計師公會：學生轉正式會員需同意警務處有權套取申請人的指模","createTime":"2020-12-07T04:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T15:51:56.000Z","uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ba6d0f9ea6370cb3378fb9228e1afb7cf8b50504","tid":2315122,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:15:06.000Z","msg":"「香港會計手足工會」在 Facebook 透露，香港會計師公會的學生會員要求申請成為正式會員時，遭公會新增要求填寫授權書，容許警務處向公會提供刑事犯罪紀錄，以及同意警務處套取申請人的指模。「手足工會」批評有關要求不必要及不合理，要求公會立即取消。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9C%83%E8%A8%88%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E6%94%B9%E5%85%A5%E6%9C%83%E6%85%A3%E4%BE%8B-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E5%93%A1%E8%BD%89%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E6%9C%83%E5%93%A1-%E9%9C%80%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%A5%97%E6%8C%87%E6%A8%A1-%E6%9F%A5%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84/?fbclid=IwAR2ilbxjxzSYcM_WiYeovTm9wLVNkOsuydOLa_8mBDX2XZq510GQVocubIs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2585%25A3%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25BD%2589%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BC%258F%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E9%259C%2580%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2584%258F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%25A5%2597%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25A8%25A1-%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%2588%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2ilbxjxzSYcM_WiYeovTm9wLVNkOsuydOLa_8mBDX2XZq510GQVocubIs&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTp1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=7801b492\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2585%25A3%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25BD%2589%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BC%258F%25E